{"tid":2112144,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"鄱陽湖掘堤壩 棄農村救武漢","createTime":"2020-07-17T05:44:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-17T06:41:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3c6cd33bf5dc945641ba98173a86f5cd419c349c","tid":2112144,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T05:44:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200717/TQAWDG3ZERWPGE6FV4K277SZ5Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200717%2FTQAWDG3ZERWPGE6FV4K277SZ5Y%2F&d=6SBmejzB2pOSQzgprEhHpfG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=b00a9eb5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200717%2FTQAWDG3ZERWPGE6FV4K277SZ5Y%2F&h=e7742169\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200717/TQAWDG3ZERWPGE6FV4K277SZ5Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n鄱陽湖掘堤壩 棄農村救武漢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/TyKbkBC3MoY9q13_KCJEpMg9aAw=/365x454/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TM42TV4IS2U7OAZ3SLEPWD3SBU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTyKbkBC3MoY9q13_KCJEpMg9aAw%3D%2F365x454%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTM42TV4IS2U7OAZ3SLEPWD3SBU.gif&h=716be5f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n挖土機挖開鄱陽湖的堤防。<br />\n<br />\n江西鄱陽湖水位受暴雨和三峽大壩全力洩洪雙重影響，未來數日恐將發生流域性大洪水，可能突破1998年歷史最高水位。傳當局要啟用長江防洪體系的「最後一道保險」，將分洪至圍江、圍湖造田的地區，被網友稱為是「保武漢，棄鄱陽」、「保城市，棄農村」。有民眾目擊，插有五星國旗的挖土機挖開鄱陽湖堤壩。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n挖土機插國旗<br />\n<br />\n水利部長江水利委員會副總工程師陳桂亞日前坦言，鄱陽湖水位達到甚至突破1998年水位的可能性很大。雖然陳強調，蓄滯洪區啟用還處於準備階段，是否全部啟用仍要看後期的決策，但前日微博上已有影片流傳，插有國旗的挖土機，拚命挖開鄱陽湖堤壩，讓洪水全湧進農田。地方報道江西省為保九江市，「主動決堤」鄱陽湖，讓湖水湧入數十萬的農田。<br />\n<br />\n另外，重慶從周二（14日）開始。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n台灣《自由時報》/中新社"},{"pid":"e2a623573346587d7b28517a54bfb3662014fab1","tid":2112144,"uid":259088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T05:45:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"96213a80c61460786e0e717466807346ab395be5","tid":2112144,"uid":253016,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T05:46:49.000Z","msg":"on9識唔識玩架支那仔<br />\n你由佢爆咪少D低口多D糧<br />\n你而家自浸農田遲D咪又係餓死"},{"pid":"562e22d1f6f76c8dae4954907d7dcc11ce51d570","tid":2112144,"uid":3122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T05:46:51.000Z","msg":"主動決堤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n偉大"},{"pid":"2ec386a9bae418cfb09b7a32d087ff94b4c1d62b","tid":2112144,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T05:47:36.000Z","msg":"蟻民<br />\n果然係等俾水浸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceab051b05f668af62b1ab4f857cd4248abadd3c","tid":2112144,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T06:41:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 終於要出最後一招喇  洪水要加油呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}